      "value": "<p>Many tieflings born of Hellâ€™s fiery depths can call forth flames to sear their foes. The tiefling can cast @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.a2zXJ84rzkD8SIBe]{Overheat} as a spell-like ability. At 11th level, the scion can instead cast @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.WP0QPu6QvApGaQIG]{Explosive Blast} as a spell-like ability. The scion can invoke hellfire this way once per day.</p>\n<p><strong>This replaces deceitful and fiendish gloom.</strong></p>\n<p><em>Use the formula <code>11 + @abilities.cha.mod</code>for the Overheat spell-like ability, and <code>13 + @abilities.cha.mod</code> for Explosive Blast.</em></p>"
